00:53:16.120 --> 00:53:19.320
They were among the last of
the enslaved with memories

00:53:19.320 --> 00:53:22.640
of their birth countries
and so direct connection

00:53:22.640 --> 00:53:24.210
to the religious traditions
they had brought

00:53:24.210 --> 00:53:26.540
with them passed with
that generation.

00:53:26.540 --> 00:53:30.240
A second reason for the
disappearance of Muslims

00:53:30.240 --> 00:53:32.700
at this point in US
history has to do

00:53:32.700 --> 00:53:35.820
with the consequences
of the Civil War.

00:53:35.820 --> 00:53:38.050
After emancipation establishment

00:53:38.050 --> 00:53:42.340
of Black churches throughout
the south begins in earnest.

00:53:42.340 --> 00:53:44.340
