focal points

00:53:44.340 --> 00:53:47.470
for newly liberated
communities while missionaries

00:53:47.470 --> 00:53:52.700 position:56%
from free Black denominations of the
north arrive both to provide support

00:53:52.700 --> 00:53:57.130
and to convert those who were
still outside of the church.

00:53:57.130 --> 00:54:00.800
Through the decades that follow,
Christianity becomes broadly

00:54:00.800 --> 00:54:04.490
and irrevocably one of the
most significant elements

00:54:04.490 --> 00:54:06.860
of African-American life.

00:54:06.860 --> 00:54:09.620
