but we can establish nones.

01:45:17.460 --> 01:45:21.970 position:56%
Number two, there is free speech
and free association and free press,

01:45:21.970 --> 01:45:25.470
and general equal protection
and due process liberty rights

01:45:25.470 --> 01:45:28.320
that folk of no faith can enjoy.

01:45:28.320 --> 01:45:32.640
Folk of faith can enjoy them too
and the question is, is that enough

01:45:32.640 --> 01:45:35.690
for those who do not have a
faith claim along the way?

01:45:35.690 --> 01:45:38.550
Those are big questions that
we're going to have to face

01:45:38.550 --> 01:45:43.000
